{"tid":86864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【外遊注意】強國出口霧霾 南韓政府急發警報","createTime":"2017-01-19T11:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T10:08:05.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b12284aef58b3aecf08dbdf4cc16ab74fccc321","tid":86864,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"【外遊注意】強國出口霧霾 南韓政府急發警報<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/19/192418_7bbec8a8733eb9bb442ac125b46cac23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F19%2F192418_7bbec8a8733eb9bb442ac125b46cac23.jpg&h=9e8b15c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYdGfNqz4fVnyAcLVVDeKqctKSGuAawEF1nN5Vt5FJXFi?filename=JiJU15b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiJU15b.jpg&h=edb2acae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/19/192419_0cc3272c98612733ce7b02c9e1661438.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F19%2F192419_0cc3272c98612733ce7b02c9e1661438.jpg&h=cd5228e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYHZGEkNDngZVqLpMXQgWciojx7JQ8qKHg39UUrc84VRp?filename=850P6Fs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F850P6Fs.jpg&h=514a45c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強國貴為「出口大國」，現在連霧霾都出口了！連續兩日南韓受來自中國的霧霾侵襲，西部地區、釜山、大邱的PM2.5指數爆錶，而且發出預警。<br />\n<br />\n中午時份，首爾時區的PM2.5指數為176，屬於中度污染，南韓多個地方的PM2.5指數亦屬於這一級別。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體指出，當局預測今日全國顆粒物濃度等級為「重度污染」等級，部分地區等級為「嚴重污染」。分析指，這次空氣污染，是因為中國霧霾隨着西北風，一路吹到南韓。早前一項研究亦指出，朝鮮半島空氣污染的來源，有一半是來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n當地部門預測，首爾、京畿道最快今晚會降雪，有望改善微塵污染。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56193214&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56193214%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170119&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2f11e157\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56193214%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170119&h=72f24da5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56193214&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170119</a>"},{"pid":"71433406f0663374af5b939387baab4964045685","tid":86864,"uid":13522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"其實有無話幾耐會散<br />\n利申：想學野"},{"pid":"1305a93ab3e4a70b3aae6616efdac3ba5f173e20","tid":86864,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.efchina.org/RestoringBlueSkies-zh/pop_science/pop_science_20160122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.efchina.org%2FRestoringBlueSkies-zh%2Fpop_science%2Fpop_science_20160122&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=58306956\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.efchina.org/RestoringBlueSkies-zh/pop_science/pop_science_20160122</a>"},{"pid":"92bd268c97d519e90e87a3151428cc334870112b","tid":86864,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"吹到去福岡未？"},{"pid":"effe79e52f2a1069ad93725e83cda9f0195a24fd","tid":86864,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"出口大國"},{"pid":"ebba099dbdfdffbb82df0df7eb628946cec5abfa","tid":86864,"uid":38552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T23:37:04.000Z","msg":"可唔可以集體告大陸謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喉嚨辛苦左幾日"},{"pid":"0d643b6ae844e1300b63de92445e993bd4485d66","tid":86864,"u